{"type":"message","id":"26d5eed5","parentId":"e9738191","timestamp":"2026-02-15T12:30:19.564Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Sun 2026-02-15 14:30 GMT+2] HOT RELOAD ACCEPTANCE TEST & FLOAT SNIPING DEPLOY.\n\n1.  **Sandbox Acceptance Test:**\n    *   Create `docs_archive/HOT_RELOAD_SANDBOX.md`.\n    *   Launch `src/test_hot_reload.py` (special script to watch this file).\n    *   *Action:* Modify file (`margin: 1.0` -> `5.0`).\n    *   *Measure:* Time delta between file write and log event.\n    *   *Integrity Check:* Ensure `DMarketClient` instance ID remains same (connection persistent).\n\n2.  **Strategy Update (Float Sniping):**\n    *   Edit `docs_archive/MASTER_PROTOCOL.md`.\n    *   *Replace:* \"Arbitrage\" -> \"Float Sniping & Market Making\".\n    *   *Define:* \"Float Sniping: Buy FT < 0.17 at market price. Sell at +15%.\"\n    *   *Trigger:* This edit should trigger the *real* Hot Reload in the background agent (if running) or prepare state for next start.\n\n3.  **Verification:**\n    *   Read logs to confirm `MASTER_PROTOCOL.md` reload event.\n    *   Verify `dmarket_api.py` still has Ed25519 logic intact.\n\n4.  **Output:**\n    *   Sandbox Response Time (ms).\n    *   Integrity Confirmation.\n    *   Final Readiness Statement."}],"timestamp":1771158619562}}
{"type":"message","id":"0f7c48e2","parentId":"26d5eed5","timestamp":"2026-02-15T12:30:27.181Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Initiating the Test**\n\nI'm currently focused on the initial setup. I've successfully created the `HOT_RELOAD_SANDBOX.md` file within the `docs_archive` directory, initializing it with the `margin: 1.0` content as per the plan. Now I'm preparing for the Hot Reload Acceptance Test.\n\n\n**Formulating the Next Steps**\n\nI've got the initial sandbox file and test setup done. Now, I'm shifting focus to creating the `src/test_hot_reload.py` file, which is key for the Hot Reload Acceptance Test. I'll need to write the test to validate the hot reload functionality itself.\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"write_1771158626947_687","name":"write","arguments":{"file_path":"docs_archive/HOT_RELOAD_SANDBOX.md","content":"# HOT RELOAD SANDBOX\nmargin: 1.0\nstatus: active\n"},"thoughtSignature":""},{"type":"toolCall","id":"write_1771158627056_688","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"import time\nimport sys\nimport os\nfrom watchdog.observers import Observer\nfrom watchdog.events import FileSystemEventHandler\n\n# Mock DMarketClient\nclass DMarketClient:\n    def __init__(self):\n        self.instance_id = id(self)\n        print(f\"DMarketClient initialized. ID: {self.instance_id}\")\n\nclient = DMarketClient()\n\nclass ConfigHandler(FileSystemEventHandler):\n    def on_modified(self, event):\n        if event.src_path.endswith(\"HOT_RELOAD_SANDBOX.md\"):\n            print(f\"Detected modification: {event.src_path}\")\n            print(f\"Time: {time.time()}\")\n            with open(event.src_path, 'r') as f:\n                content = f.read()\n                print(f\"New Content: {content.strip()}\")\n            print(f\"Client ID check: {client.instance_id}\")\n\nif __name__ == \"__main__\":\n    path = \"docs_archive\"\n    event_handler = ConfigHandler()\n    observer = Observer()\n    observer.schedule(event_handler, path, recursive=False)\n    observer.start()\n    print(f\"Watching {path}/HOT_RELOAD_SANDBOX.md for changes...\")\n    \n    try:\n        while True:\n            time.sleep(1)\n    except KeyboardInterrupt:\n        observer.stop()\n    observer.join()\n","file_path":"src/test_hot_reload.py"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"exec_1771158627175_689","name":"exec","arguments":{"background":true,"command":"python src/test_hot_reload.py"}}],"api":"google-vertex","provider":"google-vertex","model":"gemini-3-pro-preview","usage":{"input":5098,"output":484,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":5582,"cost":{"input":0.010196,"output":0.005808,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.016004}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1771158619563}}
