{"type":"message","id":"6c9d5a5a","parentId":"7407ba71","timestamp":"2026-02-15T12:31:16.545Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Observing Performance Metrics**\n\nThe hot reload is still lightning fast, clocking in around 8ms. The client ID integrity check also remained consistent. Seems like all systems are go.\n\n\n**Initiating Protocol Revisions**\n\nI've successfully updated the master protocol documentation, renaming the section to \"Float Sniping & Market Making\" and defining the float sniping strategy. Now, I'm verifying the Ed25519 logic within `dmarket_api.py` to ensure it's still intact.\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"edit_1771158676540_696","name":"edit","arguments":{"file_path":"docs_archive/MASTER_PROTOCOL.md","oldText":"Arbitrage","newText":"Float Sniping & Market Making\nFloat Sniping: Buy FT < 0.17 at market price. Sell at +15%."},"thoughtSignature":""}],"api":"google-vertex","provider":"google-vertex","model":"gemini-3-pro-preview","usage":{"input":7053,"output":256,"cacheRead":5229,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":7309,"cost":{"input":0.014105999999999999,"output":0.003072,"cacheRead":0.0010458000000000002,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0182238}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1771158668316}}
